MALACAÑANG RESIDENCE OF THE PRESIDENT OF THE PHILIPPINES MANILA

PROCLAMATION NO. 630

AMENDING PROCLAMATION NO. 361 DATED MARCH 6, 1968, RESERVING FOR INDUSTRIAL PURPOSES A PARCEL OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN IN LAMAO, MUNICIPALITY OF LIMAY, PROVINCE OF BATAAN.

By virtue of the powers vested in me by law, I, FERDINAND E. MARCOS, President of the Philippines, do hereby amend Proclamation No. 361 dated March 6, 1968, by enlarging the area covered and reserving the same for industrial purposes including the establishment of an industrial estate, subject to private rights, if any there be, under the administration of the National Development Company or a subsidiary thereof organized for such purposes, which land is more particularly described as follows (pending the fixing of its permanent boundaries after an accurate survey by more precise instruments):

